title: GDG DevFest 2016 Announced
brief: Google Developers Group Yangon is proud to announce the second annual GDG DevFest 2016 which is the biggest Google related event in Myanmar carefully crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **12-13th of November** in **Yangon**.

title: Call for Papers Time
brief: GDG DevFest Yangon 2016 announced! The 2th edition of the biggest conference about Google technologies in Myanmar will take on **November 12-13** in a largest city of Myanmar. That means that it is time to open [call for talk submissions](http://goo.gl/aMIPH8).
